## **Trends Summary Across the Pairs (Down the Group)**

| Property              | Trend                        | Explanation                                                                        |
| --------------------- | ---------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Orbital Number**    | Increases                    | Each period adds a new shell                                                       |
| **Oxidation States**  | Expandable in lower elements | Heavier elements (Period 3) can use **d-orbitals** to show higher oxidation states |
| **Electronegativity** | Decreases                    | Increased atomic size + shielding → lower nuclear pull on bonding electrons        |

